*Mazzaroths* -- the TWELVE SIGNS (xxxviii., 31, 32), which words, if
they mean anything, imply knowledge of the Zodiac even among the nomadic
Arabic tribes. The *Book of Job*, they say, precedes Homer and Hesiod by
