*Cesil* (Orion); and that of the *desert* rains with reference to
*Scorpio*, the eighth constellation; and found that in presence the
eternal conformity of those divisions of the zodiac and names of the
planets applied in the same order everywhere and always; and in presence
of the impossibility of attributing it all to chance and *coincidence*,

